This project is a clean and modern restaurant menu app design focused on easy navigation and user comfort.

🔹 Flash Screen – A quick, welcoming splash screen.
🔹 Home Page – Includes an image carousel to showcase popular dishes and offers.
🔹 5 Food Categories – Neatly organized for smooth browsing.
🔹 Signup & Login Pages – Feature image carousels for an engaging entry experience.
🔹 Search & Favourites – Helps users find and save their favorite dishes.
🔹 Item Description Page – Shows dish details with images and price.
🔹 Cart & Payment Pages – Simple, clear, and user-friendly checkout process.

Designed with a focus on clarity, flow, and a smooth user experience. 🍔📲
